    "long_instructions": "### Call and Response Challenge: Improv & Timing\r\n\r\nIn live music, performers often respond to each other in the moment—just like a jazz musician improvising a solo or a DJ remixing a track on the fly. In this challenge, you'll practice improvisation and timing by interacting with your music in real-time.\r\n\r\n**Do This**:\r\n- Create a backtrack with a steady beat or melody.\r\n- Code a trigger that plays a small loop.\r\n- Perform live! Each time you use the trigger, modify the loop—change the sound, adjust the effect, or change up the timing.",
